{"tid":490685,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"遊客爬酒店露台失足　下身插落鐵枝慘死","createTime":"2017-12-06T00:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T04:12:17.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93dbe28342d8451685eceaa3dcc8e46b7e63a492","tid":490685,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:05:25.000Z","msg":"泰國芭堤雅一名俄羅斯男遊客遺失酒店房間門匙後，竟然爬酒店外牆想由露台進入房間，豈料失足跌落防盜鐵枝，插入下身和腿部血流不止，他痛苦大叫，送院後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n俄籍男子大約凌晨4時返回酒店時發現遺失門匙，無法返回位於4樓的房間，他拍門叫醒鄰房人客，冒險企圖由露台爬回自己房間，可是不慎失足，腿部插入酒店安裝的鐵尖上，令他懸在半空，傷口流出的鮮血染紅了白色外牆。<br />\n<br />\n救援人員到場後，先以繩索固定男子身體及安排他吸氧氣，其後鋸斷插在他腿上的鐵枝，以吊臂車把他運回地面並送往附近醫院，但男子送院後數小時證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n一名目擊者表示：「我當時聽到他的呻吟聲，他非常痛苦又驚慌。這件事很可悲，而且是可以避免的。他應該等到酒店接待處早上開放時，向他們要求新門匙。」據知，涉事酒店正是為了防止住客爬牆進入房間，才在露台邊安裝鐵尖。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171202/large/1512183770_2664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F1512183770_2664.jpg&h=7f9fcd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171202/large/1512183772_f946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F1512183772_f946.jpg&h=4a7ca2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171202/large/1512183773_ae68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F1512183773_ae68.jpg&h=268532d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171202/57531203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57531203&d=3%2F5YkPlJbG%2BQjCW%2B8PjjmQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=91ce0a41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57531203&h=6893d1f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171202/57531203</a>"},{"pid":"b634ab9290b22275c1be59012a908a4f521a0651","tid":490685,"uid":71323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:08:13.000Z","msg":"隔離房房客會唔會俾人告？"},{"pid":"0c1220cc293a5bdc3ddcb7eaa1082dad1d8e1d75","tid":490685,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:08:52.000Z","msg":"睇圖都覺痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290412a66a9ec97eb7ed94e0e66637f8c7dd65bd","tid":490685,"uid":53145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泰國芭堤雅一名俄羅斯男遊客遺失酒店房間門匙後，竟然爬酒店外牆想由露台進入房間，豈料失足跌落防盜鐵枝，插入下身和腿部血流不止，他痛苦大叫，送院後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n俄籍男子大約凌晨4時返回酒店時發現遺失門匙，無法返回位於4樓的房間，他拍門叫醒鄰房人客，冒險企圖由露台爬回自己房間，可是不慎失足，腿部插入酒店安裝的鐵尖上，令他懸在半空，傷口流出的鮮血染紅了白色外牆。<br />\n<br />\n救援人員到場後，先以繩索固定男子身體及安排他吸氧氣，其後鋸斷插在他腿上的鐵枝，以吊臂車把他運回地面並送往附近醫院，但男子送院後數小時證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n一名目擊者表示：「我當時聽到他的呻吟聲，他非常痛苦又驚慌。這件事很可悲，而且是可以避免的。他應該等到酒店接待處早上開放時，向他們要求新門匙。」據知，涉事酒店正是為了防止住客爬牆進入房間，才在露台邊安裝鐵尖。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171202/large/1512183770_2664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F1512183770_2664.jpg&h=7f9fcd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171202/large/1512183772_f946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F1512183772_f946.jpg&h=4a7ca2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171202/large/1512183773_ae68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%